    {
      "id": "el_5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 125,
      "width": 406,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "Number = 10a+b, Reversed = 10b+a, Diff = 9(a-b)\nLarger = (S+D)/2, Smaller = (S-D)/2\n\nHCF = lowest powers of common primes\nLCM = highest powers of ALL primes\nHCF x LCM = Product of two numbers\n\nHCF of fracs = HCF(num)/LCM(den)\nLCM of fracs = LCM(num)/HCF(den)\n\nLargest N dividing X,Y leaving rem R = HCF(X-R, Y-R)\nSmallest N div by X,Y leaving rem R = LCM(X,Y) + R",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 500,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 5,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f0"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Number = 10a+b, Reversed = 10b+a, Diff = 9(a-b)\nLarger = (S+D)/2, Smaller = (S-D)/2\n\nHCF = lowest powers of common primes\nLCM = highest powers of ALL primes\nHCF x LCM = Product of two numbers\n\nHCF of fracs = HCF(num)/LCM(den)\nLCM of fracs = LCM(num)/HCF(den)\n\nLargest N dividing X,Y leaving rem R = HCF(X-R, Y-R)\nSmallest N div by X,Y leaving rem R = LCM(X,Y) + R",
      "autoResize": true,
