    {
      "id": "el_8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 125,
      "width": 398,
      "height": 172,
      "text": "Div by 3,9 -> digit sum | by 4 -> last 2 digits\nDiv by 8 -> last 3 | by 11 -> |odd-even pos sum|\nDiv by 6 = 2 AND 3 | by 12 = 3 AND 4\n\nUnit digit cycle (period 4): 2->2,4,8,6  3->3,9,7,1\n7->7,9,3,1  8->8,4,2,6 | Period 2: 4->4,6  9->9,1\nPeriod 1: 0,1,5,6 (always same)\nFind n mod period -> pick from cycle (0 = last)\n\nDigits in a^n = floor(n x log10(a)) + 1\n(a5)^2 = a(a+1) followed by 25  e.g. 35^2=1225",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 800,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 8,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f1"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Div by 3,9 -> digit sum | by 4 -> last 2 digits\nDiv by 8 -> last 3 | by 11 -> |odd-even pos sum|\nDiv by 6 = 2 AND 3 | by 12 = 3 AND 4\n\nUnit digit cycle (period 4): 2->2,4,8,6  3->3,9,7,1\n7->7,9,3,1  8->8,4,2,6 | Period 2: 4->4,6  9->9,1\nPeriod 1: 0,1,5,6 (always same)\nFind n mod period -> pick from cycle (0 = last)\n\nDigits in a^n = floor(n x log10(a)) + 1\n(a5)^2 = a(a+1) followed by 25  e.g. 35^2=1225",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
