    {
      "id": "el_23",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 682,
      "width": 328,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "Train -> Pole/Person: D = L (train length)\nTrain -> Platform: D = L + P\nTwo trains crossing: D = L1 + L2\nTrain inside tunnel: D = Tunnel - L\nTrain exit tunnel: D = Tunnel + L\n\nSame dir (overtake): Rel = S1 - S2\nOpposite dir (cross): Rel = S1 + S2\n\nEqual trains cross pole in T1,T2:\n  Opp crossing = 2.T1.T2/(T1+T2)\n  Same crossing = 2.T1.T2/(T1-T2)",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 2300,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 23,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f6"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Train -> Pole/Person: D = L (train length)\nTrain -> Platform: D = L + P\nTwo trains crossing: D = L1 + L2\nTrain inside tunnel: D = Tunnel - L\nTrain exit tunnel: D = Tunnel + L\n\nSame dir (overtake): Rel = S1 - S2\nOpposite dir (cross): Rel = S1 + S2\n\nEqual trains cross pole in T1,T2:\n  Opp crossing = 2.T1.T2/(T1+T2)\n  Same crossing = 2.T1.T2/(T1-T2)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
