    {
      "id": "el_26",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 682,
      "width": 398,
      "height": 172,
      "text": "Downstream = B + S | Upstream = B - S\nB = (Down+Up)/2 | S = (Down-Up)/2\n\nRound trip time = D/(B+S) + D/(B-S) = 2DB/(B^2-S^2)\nAvg speed round trip = (B^2-S^2)/B\n\nSame dist, diff times:\n  T_up/T_down = (B+S)/(B-S)\n\nBoat speed doubles -> new speeds = (2B+S) & (2B-S)\n  NOT 2(B+S) and 2(B-S)!",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 2600,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 26,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f7"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Downstream = B + S | Upstream = B - S\nB = (Down+Up)/2 | S = (Down-Up)/2\n\nRound trip time = D/(B+S) + D/(B-S) = 2DB/(B^2-S^2)\nAvg speed round trip = (B^2-S^2)/B\n\nSame dist, diff times:\n  T_up/T_down = (B+S)/(B-S)\n\nBoat speed doubles -> new speeds = (2B+S) & (2B-S)\n  NOT 2(B+S) and 2(B-S)!",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
