    {
      "id": "el_29",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 682,
      "width": 398,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "Work = Efficiency x Time\nIf A does in n days -> rate = 1/n per day\nTotal Work = LCM of all given days\nEff = LCM / days | Together = LCM / (sum of eff)\n\nMDH: M1.D1.H1/W1 = M2.D2.H2/W2\nEff ratio = inverse of time ratio\nWages split by EFFICIENCY ratio (not days!)\n\nn days -> (100/n)% per day\nAlternate days: find 2-day cycle work, then count\nx Men = y Women = z Children -> convert to one unit",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 2900,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 29,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f8"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Work = Efficiency x Time\nIf A does in n days -> rate = 1/n per day\nTotal Work = LCM of all given days\nEff = LCM / days | Together = LCM / (sum of eff)\n\nMDH: M1.D1.H1/W1 = M2.D2.H2/W2\nEff ratio = inverse of time ratio\nWages split by EFFICIENCY ratio (not days!)\n\nn days -> (100/n)% per day\nAlternate days: find 2-day cycle work, then count\nx Men = y Women = z Children -> convert to one unit",
      "autoResize": true,
