    {
      "id": "el_32",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 945,
      "width": 383,
      "height": 172,
      "text": "Fill pipe = +1/a | Leak/outlet = -1/b\nNet rate = 1/a - 1/b | Time = ab/(b-a)\n\nTwo fill pipes: Time = ab/(a+b)\nLeak rate = ab/(b-a) [a=without, b=with leak]\n\nPipe A+B fill in 6h, B+C in 8h, A+C in 12h:\n  2(A+B+C) = 1/6+1/8+1/12 -> solve\n\nAlternate pipes: work per cycle, count cycles\nNet > 0 -> fills | Net < 0 -> empties/never fills",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 3200,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 32,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f9"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Fill pipe = +1/a | Leak/outlet = -1/b\nNet rate = 1/a - 1/b | Time = ab/(b-a)\n\nTwo fill pipes: Time = ab/(a+b)\nLeak rate = ab/(b-a) [a=without, b=with leak]\n\nPipe A+B fill in 6h, B+C in 8h, A+C in 12h:\n  2(A+B+C) = 1/6+1/8+1/12 -> solve\n\nAlternate pipes: work per cycle, count cycles\nNet > 0 -> fills | Net < 0 -> empties/never fills",
      "autoResize": true,
