    {
      "id": "el_35",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 945,
      "width": 414,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "x% of y = xy/100 | What % is X of Y = (X/Y) x 100\n% Inc = (New-Old)/Old x 100\n\nSuccessive a% then b%: Net = a+b+ab/100\n+x% then -x% = -(x^2/100)% LOSS always\n\nA is x% more than B: B less by x/(100+x) x 100%\nPrice up x% -> reduce consumption x/(100+x) x 100%\n\nPopulation: P(1+r/100)^n | Depreciation: P(1-r/100)^n\nElection margin% = 2 x Winner% - 100\n1/2=50% 1/3=33.3% 1/4=25% 1/5=20% 1/8=12.5%",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 3500,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 35,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f10"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "x% of y = xy/100 | What % is X of Y = (X/Y) x 100\n% Inc = (New-Old)/Old x 100\n\nSuccessive a% then b%: Net = a+b+ab/100\n+x% then -x% = -(x^2/100)% LOSS always\n\nA is x% more than B: B less by x/(100+x) x 100%\nPrice up x% -> reduce consumption x/(100+x) x 100%\n\nPopulation: P(1+r/100)^n | Depreciation: P(1-r/100)^n\nElection margin% = 2 x Winner% - 100\n1/2=50% 1/3=33.3% 1/4=25% 1/5=20% 1/8=12.5%",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
