    {
      "id": "el_41",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1208,
      "width": 351,
      "height": 172,
      "text": "Direct prop: A1/A2 = B1/B2 (same order)\nInverse prop: A1/A2 = B2/B1 (flip right side)\n\nMixed chain: identify each variable as D or I\n  Direct -> same order ratio\n  Inverse -> flipped ratio\n  Multiply all ratios for answer\n\nMDH: M1.D1.H1 = M2.D2.H2 (same work)\nMore men -> fewer days (inverse)\nMore work -> more days (direct)",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 4100,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 41,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f12"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Direct prop: A1/A2 = B1/B2 (same order)\nInverse prop: A1/A2 = B2/B1 (flip right side)\n\nMixed chain: identify each variable as D or I\n  Direct -> same order ratio\n  Inverse -> flipped ratio\n  Multiply all ratios for answer\n\nMDH: M1.D1.H1 = M2.D2.H2 (same work)\nMore men -> fewer days (inverse)\nMore work -> more days (direct)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
