    {
      "id": "el_50",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1455,
      "width": 398,
      "height": 141,
      "text": "Wages split by EFFICIENCY, not days worked\nIf different days worked: split by actual work done\n  Work done = efficiency x days worked\n\nDaily wage = Total / (Men x Days)\nPiece rate: Net = accepted x rate - rejected x\npenalty\nOvertime: OT rate = normal rate x multiplier\n  Total = base pay + OT hrs x OT rate",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 5000,
