    {
      "id": "el_59",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1718,
      "width": 367,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "SI = P.R.T/100 | A = P + SI = P(1 + RT/100)\nP = 100.SI/(R.T) | R = 100.SI/(P.T) | T =\n100.SI/(P.R)\n\nDoubles: R.T = 100 | N times: R.T = (N-1) x 100\nTime to double = 100/R\n\nTwo amounts A1(T1), A2(T2):\n  SI/yr = (A2-A1)/(T2-T1), P = A1 - SI/yr x T1\n\nSplit sum equal SI: P1/P2 = R2.T2/(R1.T1)\nBorrow & Lend gain = P x (Lend% - Borrow%)/100",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 5900,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 59,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f18"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "SI = P.R.T/100 | A = P + SI = P(1 + RT/100)\nP = 100.SI/(R.T) | R = 100.SI/(P.T) | T =\n100.SI/(P.R)\n\nDoubles: R.T = 100 | N times: R.T = (N-1) x 100\nTime to double = 100/R\n\nTwo amounts A1(T1), A2(T2):\n  SI/yr = (A2-A1)/(T2-T1), P = A1 - SI/yr x T1\n\nSplit sum equal SI: P1/P2 = R2.T2/(R1.T1)\nBorrow & Lend gain = P x (Lend% - Borrow%)/100",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
