    {
      "id": "el_62",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1718,
      "width": 367,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "A = P(1+R/100)^T | CI = A - P\nHalf-yearly: R/2, 2T periods\nQuarterly: R/4, 4T periods\n\nCI-SI (2yr) = P(R/100)^2\nCI-SI (3yr) = P(R/100)^2 x (3+R/100)\n\nRule of 72: doubles in ~72/R years\nDoubles in n yrs -> 4x in 2n, 8x in 3n\n\nDiff rates: A = P(1+R1/100)(1+R2/100)(1+R3/100)\nKey: (1.1)^2=1.21 (1.1)^3=1.331 (0.8)^3=0.512",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 6200,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 62,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f19"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "A = P(1+R/100)^T | CI = A - P\nHalf-yearly: R/2, 2T periods\nQuarterly: R/4, 4T periods\n\nCI-SI (2yr) = P(R/100)^2\nCI-SI (3yr) = P(R/100)^2 x (3+R/100)\n\nRule of 72: doubles in ~72/R years\nDoubles in n yrs -> 4x in 2n, 8x in 3n\n\nDiff rates: A = P(1+R1/100)(1+R2/100)(1+R3/100)\nKey: (1.1)^2=1.21 (1.1)^3=1.331 (0.8)^3=0.512",
