      "originalText": "P(E) = favorable / total | 0 <= P(E) <= 1\nP(A or B) = P(A)+P(B)-P(A and B)\nP(A and B) = P(A) x P(B) [independent]\nP(not A) = 1-P(A) | P(at least 1) = 1-P(none)\n\n1 coin=2, n coins=2^n | 1 die=6, 2 dice=36\n52 cards: 4 suits x 13 values\n\nOdds a:b -> P = a/(a+b)\nE(X) = Sum[value x probability]\nWithout replacement: prob changes each draw",
      "autoResize": true,
