    {
      "id": "el_71",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1981,
      "width": 406,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "Odd days = total days mod 7\nOrdinary yr = 1 odd day | Leap yr = 2 odd days\n\nCentury odd days: 100->5, 200->3, 300->1, 400->0\nDay codes: 0=Sun 1=Mon 2=Tue 3=Wed 4=Thu 5=Fri 6=Sat\n\nLeap: div4 YES, div100 NO -> Leap\n  div100 YES -> must div400 for Leap\n  1900=Not, 2000=Leap\n\nDay = (century + years + months + day) mod 7\nSame calendar: ordinary +6/+11/+11, leap every 28yr",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 7100,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 71,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f22"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Odd days = total days mod 7\nOrdinary yr = 1 odd day | Leap yr = 2 odd days\n\nCentury odd days: 100->5, 200->3, 300->1, 400->0\nDay codes: 0=Sun 1=Mon 2=Tue 3=Wed 4=Thu 5=Fri 6=Sat\n\nLeap: div4 YES, div100 NO -> Leap\n  div100 YES -> must div400 for Leap\n  1900=Not, 2000=Leap\n\nDay = (century + years + months + day) mod 7\nSame calendar: ordinary +6/+11/+11, leap every 28yr",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
