    {
      "id": "el_74",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1981,
      "width": 398,
      "height": 172,
      "text": "Angle = |30H - 5.5M| (take smaller if >180)\nHour = 0.5 deg/min | Minute = 6 deg/min\n\nHands at angle theta between H and H+1:\n  M = (30H +/- theta) x 2/11\n\n12hr: Overlaps=11, Right angles=22, Straight=11\n24hr: double above | Gap between overlaps = 65m 27s\n\nMirror time = (11-H):(60-M)\nGains x min/hr -> correct again in 720/x hours",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 7400,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 74,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f23"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Angle = |30H - 5.5M| (take smaller if >180)\nHour = 0.5 deg/min | Minute = 6 deg/min\n\nHands at angle theta between H and H+1:\n  M = (30H +/- theta) x 2/11\n\n12hr: Overlaps=11, Right angles=22, Straight=11\n24hr: double above | Gap between overlaps = 65m 27s\n\nMirror time = (11-H):(60-M)\nGains x min/hr -> correct again in 720/x hours",
