    {
      "id": "el_92",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 2475,
      "width": 383,
      "height": 172,
      "text": "EJOTY anchors: E=5 J=10 O=15 T=20 Y=25\nReverse: A=26 B=25...M=14 N=13...Z=1\nMirror pairs (sum=27): A-Z B-Y C-X...M-N\n\nDetect pattern: write positions, find diffs\nConstant diff -> uniform shift (Caesar cipher)\nSum = 27 each pair -> mirror/opposite coding\nNew pos = (Old + shift - 1) mod 26 + 1\n\nNumber coding: digit operations or position-based\nCondition-based: vowels vs consonants differ",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 9200,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 92,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f29"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "EJOTY anchors: E=5 J=10 O=15 T=20 Y=25\nReverse: A=26 B=25...M=14 N=13...Z=1\nMirror pairs (sum=27): A-Z B-Y C-X...M-N\n\nDetect pattern: write positions, find diffs\nConstant diff -> uniform shift (Caesar cipher)\nSum = 27 each pair -> mirror/opposite coding\nNew pos = (Old + shift - 1) mod 26 + 1\n\nNumber coding: digit operations or position-based\nCondition-based: vowels vs consonants differ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
