        "f31"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Seating Arrangement",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_98",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 2722,
      "width": 383,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "Linear: Nth from right = Total - N + 1\nCircular: (N-1)! arrangements, fix 1 then arrange\nrest\nOpposite seat = current + N/2 (N must be even)\n\nFacing CENTER: Left = Clockwise, Right = Anti-CW\nFacing OUTSIDE: Left = Anti-CW, Right = Clockwise\n  (REVERSED from facing center!)\n\nTwo rows facing each other: left/right = own\nperspective\nFix definite clues first, then apply constraints",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
