      "originalText": "Linear: Nth from right = Total - N + 1\nCircular: (N-1)! arrangements, fix 1 then arrange\nrest\nOpposite seat = current + N/2 (N must be even)\n\nFacing CENTER: Left = Clockwise, Right = Anti-CW\nFacing OUTSIDE: Left = Anti-CW, Right = Clockwise\n  (REVERSED from facing center!)\n\nTwo rows facing each other: left/right = own\nperspective\nFix definite clues first, then apply constraints",
      "autoResize": true,
