    {
      "id": "el_101",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 2722,
      "width": 406,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "4 types: A(All) E(No) I(Some) O(Some-not)\nAll A are B -> A inside B | No A are B -> separate\n\nChains: A+A=A | A+E=E | I+A=I | I+E=O\nAll+Some = NO conclusion | Some+Some = NO conclusion\n\nConversion: All->Some(reverse) | No->No(reverse)\nSome->Some(reverse) | Some-not -> NO conversion\nTRAP: All A are B does NOT mean All B are A\n\n\"Only A are B\" = All B are A\n\"Not all A are B\" = Some A are not B",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 10100,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 101,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f32"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "4 types: A(All) E(No) I(Some) O(Some-not)\nAll A are B -> A inside B | No A are B -> separate\n\nChains: A+A=A | A+E=E | I+A=I | I+E=O\nAll+Some = NO conclusion | Some+Some = NO conclusion\n\nConversion: All->Some(reverse) | No->No(reverse)\nSome->Some(reverse) | Some-not -> NO conversion\nTRAP: All A are B does NOT mean All B are A\n\n\"Only A are B\" = All B are A\n\"Not all A are B\" = Some A are not B",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
