    {
      "id": "el_107",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 3000,
      "width": 406,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "Elimination table: cross off impossible, one per\nrow/col\nContrapositive: If A->B then NOT B->NOT A (VALID)\nInverse: NOT A->NOT B (INVALID)\n\nOrdering: chain comparisons through linking elements\n  A>B, B>C -> A>B>C (need N-1 links for N items)\n\nSelection: \"If A then B\" -> pick A -> must pick B\n  Contrapositive: drop B -> must drop A\n\"At least one\" = OR | \"At most one\" = not both\n\"Exactly one\" = XOR (one in, one out)",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 10700,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 107,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f34"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Elimination table: cross off impossible, one per\nrow/col\nContrapositive: If A->B then NOT B->NOT A (VALID)\nInverse: NOT A->NOT B (INVALID)\n\nOrdering: chain comparisons through linking elements\n  A>B, B>C -> A>B>C (need N-1 links for N items)\n\nSelection: \"If A then B\" -> pick A -> must pick B\n  Contrapositive: drop B -> must drop A\n\"At least one\" = OR | \"At most one\" = not both\n\"Exactly one\" = XOR (one in, one out)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
